name: Magnet Ape Epsilon
desc: When a "Magnet" monster on the field is destroyed: This card gains 400 ATK, until the end of this turn.

name: Magnet Reborn
desc: Pay 500 Life Points to target 1 "Magnet" monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon that target.

name: Wave of Ill Intent
desc: Each time a monster you control is destroyed by battle, inflict 300 damage to your opponent.

name: Ancient Gear Statue
desc: You can Tribute this face-up card you control; Special Summon 1 "Ancient Gear Golem" from your hand, ignoring the Summoning conditions.

name: Shockwave
desc: Activate only while your Life Points are lower than your opponent's. Select 1 monster on the field, and destroy it. Then, inflict damage to both players equal to its ATK.

name: Immortal Class
desc: Tribute 2 monsters. Special Summon 1 Level 7 or higher monster from your Graveyard (this can include "Uria, Lord of Searing Flames", "Hamon, Lord of Striking Thunder", or "Raviel, Lord of Phantasms", ignoring the Summoning conditions).

name: Sacred Knight's Shield Bearer
desc: When this card is Normal Summoned, you can remove from play 1 LIGHT Warrior-Type monster in your Graveyard to draw 1 card.

name: Sacred Knight's Spearholder
desc: You can Tribute this face-up card on the field to add 1 Equip Spell Card from your Deck to your hand.

name: Horse of the Floral Knights
desc: When this card is Normal Summoned, you can add 1 "Sacred Knight's Spearholder" or 1 "Polymerization" from your Deck to your hand.

name: Centaur Mina
desc:
"Sacred Knight's Spearholder" + "Horse of the Floral Knights"
Once during each of your turns, you can negate the activation of an opponent's Trap Card, and return it to its original position.

name: École de Zone
desc: Non-Token monsters cannot attack directly. When a non-Token monster is Normal or Special Summoned: Destroy that monster and Special Summon 1 "Mask Token" (Spellcaster-Type/DARK/Level 1/ATK ?/DEF ?) to the destroyed monster's controller's side of the field, in the same battle position as the monster destroyed by this effect. The ATK and DEF of the "Mask Token" are equal to the respective ATK and DEF of the destroyed monster.

name: Mask Token
desc: Summoned by the effect of "École de Zone"

name: Soul-Binding Gate
desc: Once per turn, when a monster that has lower ATK than your Life Points is Summoned face-up on the field, destroy that monster, and inflict 800 damage to each player.

name: Curse Reflection Doll
desc: Activate only when an effect that inflicts damage to you is activated. Switch the damage to your opponent, instead.

name: Instant Overlay
desc: Target 1 Xyz Monster on the field with no Xyz Material; attach this card to it as an Xyz Material.

name: Overlay World
desc: During each End Phase, if a player does not control an Xyz Monster: That player takes 500 damage. Xyz Monsters on the field cannot be destroyed by card effects. If an Xyz Monster is destroyed by battle, banish it instead of sending it to the Graveyard.

name: Infinite Prison
desc: Once per turn: You can discard 1 card from your hand to the Graveyard to target 1 Level 4 or lower monster in your Graveyard; place it face-up in your Spell & Trap Card Zone as a Spell Card. If this card is destroyed and sent to the Graveyard: Return all monsters placed by this card's effect in your Spell & Trap Card Zone to the hand.

name: Chaos Bloom
desc: This card gains effects based on the number of cards with the same name in your Graveyard. ● 0: Destroy 1 face-up monster on the field with 1000 or less ATK. ● 1: Destroy 1 Spell/Trap Card on the field. ● 2: Destroy 1 card on the field.

name: Highrate Draw
desc: Destroy all monsters you control. Then, draw 1 card for each Machine-Type monster destroyed by this effect.

name: Ulevo
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. This card must be Tribute Summoned by offering 3 Winged Beast-Type monsters on your side of the field as Tributes. If this card attacks your opponent's Life Points directly and makes them 0, the controller of this card wins the Match.

name: Meteo the Matchless
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. This card must be Tribute Summoned by offering 3 Beast-Warrior-Type monsters on your side of the field as Tributes. If this card attacks your opponent's Life Points directly and makes them 0, the controller of this card wins the Match.

name: King of Destruction - Xexex
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. This card must be Tribute Summoned by Tributing 3 Fiend-Type monsters on your side of the field. If this card attacks your opponent's Life Points directly and makes them 0, the controller of this card wins the Match.

name: Queen of Fate - Eternia
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. This card must be Tribute Summoned by Tributing 3 Fairy-Type monsters on your side of the field. If this card attacks your opponent's Life Points directly and makes them 0, the controller of this card wins the Match.

name: Testament of the Arcane Lords
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. This card must be Tribute Summoned by Tributing 3 Spellcaster-Type monsters on your side of the field. If this card attacks your opponent's Life Points directly and makes them 0, the controller of this card wins the Match.

name: Armament of the Lethal Lords
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. This card must be Tribute Summoned by Tributing 3 Warrior-Type monsters on your side of the field. If this card attacks your opponent's Life Points directly and makes them 0, the controller of this card wins the Match.

name: Chimaera, the Master of Beasts
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. To Tribute Summoned this card, you must Tribute 3 Beast-Type monsters. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, you win the Match.

name: Emperor of Lightning
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. This card must be Tribute Summoned by Tributing 3 Thunder-Type monsters on your side of the field. If this card attacks your opponent's Life Points directly and makes them 0, the controller of this card wins the Match.

name: Tyr, the Vanquishing Warlord
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. To Tribute Summon this card, you must Tribute 3 Fairy-Type monsters. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, you win the Match.

name: Lorelei, the Symphonic Arsenal
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. To Tribute Summon this card, you must Tribute 3 Machine-Type monsters. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, you win the Match.

name: Aggiba, the Malevolent Sh'nn S'yo
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. To Tribute Summon this card you must Tribute 3 Fiend-Type monsters. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, you win the Match.

name: Skuna, the Leonine Rakan
desc: This card cannot be Special Summoned. To Tribute Summon this card you must Tribute 3 Beast-Warrior-Type monsters. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, you win the Match.

name: Stardust Divinity
desc:
1 LIGHT Tuner + 2 or more non-Tuner Fairy-Type monsters
This card cannot be Special Summoned except by Synchro Summon. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, you win the Match.

name: Grizzly, the Red Star Beast
desc:
1 EARTH Tuner + 2 or more non-Tuner Beast-Type monsters
This card cannot be Special Summoned except by Synchro Summon. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, you win the Match.

name: King Landia the Goldfang
desc:
3 Level 8 monsters 
 Must be Xyz Summoned and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, while it has an Xyz Material attached that was originally Beast-Warrior-Type, you win the Match.

name: Queen Nereia the Silvercrown
desc:
3 Level 6 monsters 
 Must be Xyz Summoned and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, while it has an Xyz Material attached that was originally Plant-Type, you win the Match.

name: Legendary Dragon of White
desc:
3 Level 8 monsters
Must be Xyz Summoned and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, while it has an Xyz Material attached that was originally Dragon-Type, you win the Match.

name: Legendary Magician of Dark
desc:
3 Level 7 monsters
Must be Xyz Summoned and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, while it has an Xyz Material attached that was originally Spellcaster-Type, you win the Match.

name: E☆HERO Pit Boss
desc:
3 Level 6 monsters
Must be Xyz Summoned and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, while it has an Xyz Material attached that was originally Spellcaster-Type, you win the Match.

name: Grandopolis, The Eternal Golden City
desc:
3 Level 8 monsters
Must be Xyz Summoned and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card attacks your opponent directly and reduces their Life Points to 0, while it has an Xyz Material attached that was originally Machine-Type, you win the Match.

name: Assault Blackwing - Kuniyoshi the Fogbow
desc:
1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner monsters
If this card was Synchro Summoned using a "Blackwing" monster as a Synchro Material, it is treated as a Tuner monster. Once per turn: You can send 1 "Blackwing" monster from your hand to the Graveyard; inflict 300 damage to your opponent.

name: Illusion Ninjitsu Art of Hazy Shuriken
desc: Activate only if you control a "Ninja" monster. If a card(s) is added to your hand, you can send 1 of those cards to the Graveyard, and if you do, inflict 300 damage to your opponent. If you control no "Ninja" monsters, destroy this card.

name: Performapal Odd-Eyes Light Phoenix
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 3
[ Pendulum Effect ]
When an opponent's monster declares a direct attack: You can destroy the card you have in your other Pendulum Zone; Special Summon this card from your Pendulum Zone.
----------------------------------------
[ Monster Effect ]
If this card would be destroyed by battle, you can destroy 1 card in your Pendulum Zone instead.

name: Performapal Odd-Eyes Unicorn
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 8
[ Pendulum Effect ]
Once per turn, when an "Odd-Eyes" monster you control declares an attack: You can target that monster; until the end of the Battle Phase, that target gains ATK equal to the ATK of 1 Attack Position "Performapal" monster you control.
----------------------------------------
[ Monster Effect ]
All "Performapal" and "Odd-Eyes" monsters you control gain 100 ATK for each "Performapal" and "Odd-Eyes" monsters you control.

name: Performapal Bot-Eyes Lizard (Mod)
desc: Once per turn, during either player's turn, if this card was Normal or Special Summoned this turn: You can activate this effect; this card's name becomes either "Odd-Eyes Dragon" or "Odd-Eyes Pendulum Dragon".

name: Abyss Actor - Devil Heel
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 1
[ Pendulum Effect ]
Once per turn: You can add 1 "Abyss Actor" Pendulum Monster you control to your Extra Deck, face-up, then target 1 monster your opponent controls; it loses ATK equal to the ATK of the monster added to your Extra Deck, until the end of this turn.
----------------------------------------
[ Monster Effect ]
If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can target 1 monster your opponent controls; it loses 1000 ATK for each "Abyss Actor" monster you currently control.

name: Abyss Actor - Big Star
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 3
[ Pendulum Effect ]
Once per turn: You can add 1 "Abyss Actor" Pendulum Monster you control to your Extra Deck, face-up, then target 1 "Abyss Script" Spell Card in your Graveyard; add it to your hand.
----------------------------------------
[ Monster Effect ]
Once per turn: You can add 1 "Abyss Script" Spell Card from your Deck to your hand, but it is sent to the Graveyard during the End Phase of this turn.

name: Abyss Actor - Funky Comedian
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 8
[ Pendulum Effect ]
Once per turn: You can add 1 "Abyss Actor" Pendulum Monster you control to your Extra Deck, face-up, then target 1 monster you control; it gains ATK equal to the ATK of the monster added to your Extra Deck, until the end of this turn.
----------------------------------------
[ Monster Effect ]
If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can have this card gain 300 ATK for each "Abyss Actor" monster you currently control.

name: Abyss Actor - Extra
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 3
[ Pendulum Effect ]
If your opponent controls a monster: You can Special Summon this card from your Pendulum Zone.
----------------------------------------
[ Monster Effect ]
You can place this card from your side of the field into your Pendulum Zone, but its Pendulum Effect cannot be activated this turn.

name: Abyss Actor - Sassy Rookie
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 2
[ Pendulum Effect ]
If this card is destroyed: You can target 1 Level 4 or lower monster your opponent controls; destroy that target.
----------------------------------------
[ Monster Effect ]
Once per turn, this card cannot be destroyed.

name: Abyss Actor - Pretty Heroine
desc:
Pendulum Scale = 2
[ Pendulum Effect ]
Once per turn, during your opponent's Battle Phase: You can target 1 monster your opponent controls that destroyed by battle 1 "Abyss Actor" monster under your control; that target loses ATK equal to the battle damage you took from that battle (this is a Quick Effect).
----------------------------------------
[ Monster Effect ]
Once per turn, during either player's Battle Phase: You can target 1 monster your opponent controls; that target loses original ATK equal the total battle damage inflicted during this Battle Phase.

name: Abyss Script - Fantasy Magic
desc: Target 1 "Abyss Actor" monster you control; this turn, if an opponent's monster battles that monster, return it to your opponent's hand after damage calculation.

name: Abyss Script - Opening Ceremony
desc: Gain 500 LP for each Attack Position "Abyss Actor" monster you control.

name: Abyss Prop - Escape Stage Coach
desc: Once per turn, during either player's Battle Phase: You can target 1 "Abyss Actor" monster you control; this turn, it cannot be destroyed by battle, also it is unaffected by an opponent's effects.

name: Fortissimo
desc: Once per turn: You can target 1 "Melodious" monster you control; it gains 600 ATK until your next Standby Phase.
